{"info": {"author": "Xolani Mazibuko", "author_email": "mazi76erx@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Environment :: Web Environment", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "==============\nMention-Python\n==============\n\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/MentionAPI.svg\n    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/MentionAPI\n\n.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/mazi76erX2/mention-python.svg?branch=master\n    :target: https://travis-ci.org/mazi76erX2/mention-python\n\n.. image:: https://codecov.io/gh/mazi76erX2/mention-python/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\n  :target: https://codecov.io/gh/mazi76erX2/mention-python\n\n.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/mention-python/badge/?version=latest\n    :target: https://mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest\n\n**A Python wrapper around the Mention API.**\n\nInstallation\n------------\n\n.. code-block:: console\n\n    $ python3 -m pip install mention\n\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    >>> from mention import FetchAMentionAPI\n    >>> first_mention = FetchAMentionAPI('access_token', 'account_id', 'alert_id', 'mention_id')\n\n    >>> first_mention_data = first_mention.query()\n\n    >>> title = first_mention_data['title']\n\nExamples\n--------\n\n**Fetch all alerts of an account**\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    >>> allAlerts = mention.FetchAlertsAPI(access_token, account_id)\n\n    >>> data = nandosAlert.query()\n\n    >>> alertsList = data['alerts']\t\n    >>> alertsList[5]['alert']['name']\n    'Nandos'\t\t\t \t\t\t\n\n    >>> data['alert']['query']['included_keywords']\n    ['Nandos', 'Flame-grilled Chicken', 'Peri-Peri Sauce']\n\n**Fetch a mention**\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    >>> nandosMention = mention.FetchAMentionAPI(access_token, account_id, alert_id, mention_id)\n\n    >>> data = nandosMention.query()\n\n    >>> data['title']\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\n    \"Nando's launches their own food ordering app\"\n\n    >>> data['description']\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\n    \"Nando's has launched their own app that will allow people to order their favourite meal from the comfort \n    ...\tof their own home.\"\n\n    >>> data['original_url']\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\n    'https:\\/\\/www.iol.co.za\\/business-report\\/technology\\/nandos-launches-their-own-food-\n    ...\tordering-app-18378360'\n\n**Read More**\n\n - `Full Documentation`_\n     - `Installation`_\n     - `Basic Usage`_\n     - `Contributing`_\n\n.. _Full Documentation: http:///mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/\n.. _Installation: http://mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pages/installation.html\n.. _Basic Usage: http:///mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pages/quickstart.html\n.. _Contributing: http:///mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pages/contributing.html\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/x-rst", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/mazi76erX2/mention-python", "keywords": "mention api examples", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "mention", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/mention/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/mention/", "project_urls": {"Coverage": "https://codecov.io/gh/mazi76erX2/mention-python", "Documentation": "https://mention-python.readthedocs.io/en/latest/", "Homepage": "https://github.com/mazi76erX2/mention-python", "Source Code": "https://github.com/mazi76erX2/mention-python"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/mention/0.1/", "requires_dist": ["requests", "requests-oauth2 (>=0.3.0)"], "requires_python": "", "summary": "A Python wrapper around the Mention API.", "version": "0.1", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/MentionAPI\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/MentionAPI.svg\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/60d56e71b57cd3c18207de75359b215fe4541242/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f707970692f762f4d656e74696f6e4150492e737667\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/mazi76erX2/mention-python\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://travis-ci.org/mazi76erX2/mention-python.svg?branch=master\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/cb89832f1859cfa14232c71983ef813614eb8c25/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e6f72672f6d617a693736657258322f6d656e74696f6e2d707974686f6e2e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://codecov.io/gh/mazi76erX2/mention-python\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://codecov.io/gh/mazi76erX2/mention-python/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/a6d9eaae7985baa96f9ffd85c2c39b343e4b7672/68747470733a2f2f636f6465636f762e696f2f67682f6d617a693736657258322f6d656e74696f6e2d707974686f6e2f6272616e63682f6d61737465722f67726170682f62616467652e737667\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://readthedocs.org/projects/mention-python/badge/?version=latest\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/c227d0652511934a48ed53bc43b145da1138d2e8/68747470733a2f2f72656164746865646f63732e6f72672f70726f6a656374732f6d656e74696f6e2d707974686f6e2f62616467652f3f76657273696f6e3d6c6174657374\"></a>\n<p><strong>A Python wrapper around the Mention API.</strong></p>\n<div id=\"installation\">\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"gp\">$</span> python3 -m pip install mention\n</pre>\n<pre><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">mention</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">FetchAMentionAPI</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">first_mention</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">FetchAMentionAPI</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'access_token'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'account_id'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'alert_id'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'mention_id'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">first_mention_data</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">first_mention</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">query</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">title</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">first_mention_data</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'title'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"examples\">\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n<p><strong>Fetch all alerts of an account</strong></p>\n<pre><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">allAlerts</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mention</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">FetchAlertsAPI</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">access_token</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">account_id</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">nandosAlert</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">query</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">alertsList</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'alerts'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">alertsList</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"p\">][</span><span class=\"s1\">'alert'</span><span class=\"p\">][</span><span class=\"s1\">'name'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"s1\">'Nandos'</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'alert'</span><span class=\"p\">][</span><span class=\"s1\">'query'</span><span class=\"p\">][</span><span class=\"s1\">'included_keywords'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'Nandos'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'Flame-grilled Chicken'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'Peri-Peri Sauce'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Fetch a mention</strong></p>\n<pre><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">nandosMention</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mention</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">FetchAMentionAPI</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">access_token</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">account_id</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">alert_id</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">mention_id</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">nandosMention</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">query</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'title'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">\"Nando's launches their own food ordering app\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'description'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">\"Nando's has launched their own app that will allow people to order their favourite meal from the comfort</span>\n<span class=\"o\">...</span> <span class=\"n\">of</span> <span class=\"n\">their</span> <span class=\"n\">own</span> <span class=\"n\">home</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'original_url'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"s1\">'https:\\/\\/www.iol.co.za\\/business-report\\/technology\\/nandos-launches-their-own-food-</span>\n<span class=\"o\">...</span> <span class=\"n\">ordering</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">app</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">18378360</span><span class=\"s1\">'</span>\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Read More</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><dl>\n<dt><a href=\"http:///mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Full Documentation</a></dt>\n<dd><ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pages/installation.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Installation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http:///mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pages/quickstart.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Basic Usage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http:///mention-python.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pages/contributing.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Contributing</a></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 4625141, "releases": {"0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "d63c7cf7c648fc69f71dc680a0020e02", "sha256": "786cf064a982f5d9745eb8332fa7f0eef06b4e9e7cec26468c1b529fbf1482e1"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "mention-0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "d63c7cf7c648fc69f71dc680a0020e02", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 8012, "upload_time": "2018-12-21T13:36:13", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2018-12-21T13:36:13.531019Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/3c/7f/6d1ea6010fd86aead9ff97fbbecbe174b3bf54ed6498202e302d4f6671f3/mention-0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "96a2187a3846094769392685936a8109", "sha256": "998db351380060ad5ca20d844398cbf5a5eac447bd809a3abbb0c9929f034a2a"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "mention-0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "96a2187a